Index.purpose-paragraph: MyanmarFontsCollection website is a website that collects Myanmar fonts in one place to make it easy for techies. The fonts on the website pages are not owned by this website. It is owned by the respective creator
Index.copyright-paragraph: If for any reason you want to remove a font from the website, you as the original creator can contact us and cancel.
Index.support-us-paragraph: Information is still being added, so there are many errors. If there are any, please let me know and if you want to be included as the original creator, please let me know through the contact form. We can also advise on other requirements.
